            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574;">7 - 14 days</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574;"><strong>24 - fasts</strong></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

